#: admin/views/tools-settings.php:75
msgid "Deep Debug"
msgstr "深度调试"

#: admin/views/tools-settings.php:76
msgid ""
"Low-level request and OAuth flow debug files are controlled from wp-"
"config.php, not saved plugin settings."
msgstr "底层请求和 OAuth 流程调试文件由 wp-config.php 控制，而不是由保存的插件设置控制。"

#: admin/views/tools-settings.php:81
msgid "Deep Debug Mode"
msgstr "深度调试模式"

#: admin/views/tools-settings.php:82
msgid ""
"Applies the wp-config.php constant only after Save Tools Settings is "
"clicked. Debug files are stored under uploads/aoauth-debug/."
msgstr "仅在点击“保存工具设置”后应用 wp-config.php 常量。调试文件存储在 uploads/aoauth-debug/ 下。"

#: admin/views/tools-settings.php:95
msgid ""
"If automatic toggling fails, place this above the \"stop editing\" line in "
"wp-config.php. Remove it after troubleshooting."
msgstr "If automatic toggling fails, place this above the \"stop editing\" line in wp-config.php. Remove it after troubleshooting."

#: admin/views/tools-settings.php:96
msgid ""
"Deep Debug is also active when AOAUTH_DEBUG is defined as true in wp-"
"config.php. Disabling from this screen removes supported aOAUTH debug "
"constants when WordPress can write to wp-config.php."
msgstr "当 wp-config.php 中 AOAUTH_DEBUG 定义为 true 时，深度调试也会处于活动状态。如果 WordPress 可写入 wp-config.php，从此屏幕禁用会移除受支持的 aOAUTH 调试常量。"

#: admin/views/tools-settings.php:97
msgid ""
"Apache and LiteSpeed use the generated .htaccess protection in uploads/"
"aoauth-debug/. Nginx ignores .htaccess, so block direct access to /wp-"
"content/uploads/aoauth-debug/ in the server block."
msgstr "Apache 和 LiteSpeed 使用 uploads/aoauth-debug/ 中生成的 .htaccess 保护。Nginx 会忽略 .htaccess，因此请在 server block 中阻止直接访问 /wp-content/uploads/aoauth-debug/。"

