"Clears temporary password-failure lockouts for account linking. Example: use "
"this after confirming a legitimate user was blocked while linking Google or "
"Microsoft."
msgstr "清除账户链接中的临时密码失败锁定。示例：确认合法用户在链接 Google 或 Microsoft 时被阻止后使用。"

#: admin/views/tools-settings.php:123
msgid "Clear Expired OAuth Temp Data"
msgstr "清除过期的 OAuth 临时数据"

#: admin/views/tools-settings.php:124
msgid ""
"Deletes expired OAuth state, nonce, and account-linking records. Example: "
"run this after interrupted sign-in tests or before handing a staging site to "
"another admin."
msgstr "删除过期的 OAuth state、nonce 和账户链接记录。示例：在中断的登录测试后，或将暂存站点交给其他管理员前运行。"

